summary:
I LOVE TAYLOR SWIFT.
I love her. I love her personallity. I love her laugh. I love her love for cats. I love her love for fans....
body:
I LOVE TAYLOR SWIFT.

I love her. I love her personallity. I love her laugh. I love her love for cats. I love her love for fans. I love that she treats us like family. I love that she is 28 and she wants to hang out with her mom and dad all the time,most people grow out of wanting to hang out with their parents. I love her creativity. I love that she cares for EVERYONE!!!! Everyone who build the stages at every show,everyone who works there that night at food places,checking tickets,showing people to their seats etc. i really mean EVERYONE. I love that she knows her worth. I love that she can handle herself like a pro. I could go on and on how much i love her . And you know what? I would put that i love her for her “fame” in the last place. NO actually it’s not even on the list. Screw her fame,screw her REPUTATION i’m here for her SOUL AND HEART AND MIND AND WISDOM AND BRAVNESS AND ON AND ON AND ON. ‼️‼️‼️‼️‼️‼️‼️‼️

summary:
Hey, @taylorswift 
Let me tell you about my lovely friend, @sergleza91 ‼️ We met at the Pasadena show, through a twitter group...
body:
Hey, @taylorswift

Let me tell you about my lovely friend, @sergleza91 ‼️ We met at the Pasadena show, through a twitter group chat! Then, six of us from the Pasadena show traveled to Pittsburgh together! Sergio has become such an invaluable friend, I am so thankful for you to have brought him into my life. He is able to go to two more shows, both nights in Arlington, making them his fourth and fifth shows for rep! For night one he’s in SECTION K, ROW 1, SEAT 18 ‼️ and his night two seat is in the works. Please find him and give him the biggest hug, it would mean the world to him 💕 @taylornation
